# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:12
translate portuguese english3_8b8bb224:

    # "The school-day goes by normally until my English class."
    "O dia letivo decorre normalmente até à minha aula de Inglês."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:13
translate portuguese english3_66510385:

    # "Mrs. McGee has us working on essays in class. Everyone is quiet, looking down at their papers."
    "A Sra. McGee pede-nos para escrevermos redações na aula. Todos estão em silêncio, com os olhos fixos nos seus papéis."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:14
translate portuguese english3_3d0d4f25:

    # "But I feel like somebody is watching me."
    "Mas sinto que alguém está a observar-me."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:17
translate portuguese english3_0ba62eb9:

    # "I look up at see Mrs. McGee gazing at me. Staring. A slight smile on her face."
    "Olho para cima e vejo a Sra. McGee a olhar para mim. A fixar-me. Com um leve sorriso no rosto."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:18
translate portuguese english3_e3525f66:

    # "I wonder what she could be thinking about?"
    "O que estaria ela a pensar?"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:21
translate portuguese english3_2d0786b4:

    # "She smiles, moving her hand close to her mouth."
    "Ela sorri, levando a mão à boca."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:22
translate portuguese english3_8c67e0d6:

    # "I look around at the other students surrounding me, but their eyes are all focused on the essays they are writing."
    "Olho à minha volta para os outros alunos que me rodeiam, mas os olhos de todos estão concentrados nas redações que estão a escrever."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:23
translate portuguese english3_342debb3:

    # "There is no doubt that Mrs. McGee's gaze is meant for me and me alone."
    "Não há dúvida de que o olhar da Sra. McGee é dirigido a mim e apenas a mim."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:26
translate portuguese english3_48f33b68:

    # "While I am looking directly at her, she slips the tip of her index finger between her plump lips, sucking it sensually."
    "Enquanto olho diretamente para ela, ela desliza a ponta do dedo indicador entre os lábios carnudos, chupando-o sensualmente."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:27
translate portuguese english3_3972cbcf:

    # "Her eyes never leave mine."
    "Os olhos dela nunca se afastam dos meus."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:28
translate portuguese english3_1596ea41:

    # "There is little doubt what she is thinking now. My cock twitches in my pants, thumping against the thin fabric."
    "Não há dúvida do que ela está a pensar agora. O meu pénis estremece nas calças, batendo contra o tecido fino."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:29
translate portuguese english3_341dee20:

    # "Then Randy, the know-it-all asshole who always has something clever to say, speaks up and breaks our trance."
    "Então o Randy, o idiota sabichão que tem sempre algo inteligente para dizer, fala e quebra o nosso transe."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:32
translate portuguese english3_52d7af01:

    # "Randy" "Mrs. McGee, my essay is done, can I leave?"
    "Randy" "Sra. McGee, terminei a minha redação, posso sair?"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:33
translate portuguese english3_937ce766:

    # "Mrs. McGee quickly looks up and straightens herself, as if she hasn't been thinking about dick for the last few minutes."
    "A Sra. McGee levanta rapidamente o olhar e endireita-se, como se não tivesse estado a pensar em pénis nos últimos minutos."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:34
translate portuguese english3_82e82c18:

    # et "Yes Randy, you can leave."
    et "Sim, Randy, podes sair."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:35
translate portuguese english3_90bacfb8:

    # et "In fact, any of you who are done with your essays, or would prefer to work on them at home, feel free to leave any time."
    et "Na verdade, qualquer um de vocês que tenha terminado a redação, ou prefira trabalhar nela em casa, sinta-se à vontade para sair a qualquer momento."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:36
translate portuguese english3_69be14c8:

    # "Most of the class stands up then and leaves, but I stay. So do Juliana and a few other people."
    "A maior parte da turma levanta-se então e sai, mas eu fico. O mesmo acontece com a Juliana e algumas outras pessoas."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:37
translate portuguese english3_dd5bdbb5:

    # "I don't really have anywhere to go before the next class anyways."
    "De qualquer forma, não tenho realmente para onde ir antes da próxima aula."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:39
translate portuguese english3_44bea0f3:

    # "So I focus on getting my essay done, occasionally looking up at Mrs. McGee."
    "Por isso, concentro-me em terminar a minha redação, olhando ocasionalmente para a Sra. McGee."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:40
translate portuguese english3_9fb697a3:

    # "She is focused on her work now, her eyes down on the desk in front of her."
    "Ela está concentrada no seu trabalho agora, com os olhos fixos na secretária à sua frente."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:41
translate portuguese english3_166c1158:

    # "At the end of class, I stand up and get ready to leave."
    "No final da aula, levanto-me e preparo-me para sair."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:44
translate portuguese english3_6f3f8621:

    # et "I appreciate you staying until the end of class."
    et "Agradeço por teres ficado até ao final da aula."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:45
translate portuguese english3_314047f4:

    # et "I know it wasn't the most exciting class today, but it's good that you're committed to learning."
    et "Sei que não foi a aula mais emocionante de hoje, mas é bom que estejas empenhado em aprender."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:49
translate portuguese english3_3c2d53ef:

    # et "I'm glad. I hope we can continue sometime."
    et "Fico contente. Espero que possamos continuar noutro momento."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:52
translate portuguese english3_b244bcae:

    # et "Don't get in too much of a hurry."
    et "Não te apresses demasiado."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:53
translate portuguese english3_398957e6:

    # et "Besides, my next class is coming in right now."
    et "Além disso, a minha próxima turma está a chegar agora."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:58
translate portuguese english3_db48971e:

    # et "Well, okay then."
    et "Bem, está bem então."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:59
translate portuguese english3_c08bcb72:

    # et "I'll see you next time, [pcname]."
    et "Até à próxima, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:60
translate portuguese english3_9259ab8b:

    # et "You have a good day."
    et "Tenha um bom dia."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:61
translate portuguese english3_66796d27:

    # pc "You too, Mrs. McGee."
    pc "Você também, Sra. McGee."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:64
translate portuguese english3_d25b195e:

    # "I leave her class and go on to my next."
    "Saio da aula dela e vou para a minha próxima."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:65
translate portuguese english3_764b5703:

    # "I can't get her out of my head though. She had definitely been coming on to me."
    "Mas não consigo tirá-la da cabeça. Ela estava definitivamente a dar em cima de mim."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:66
translate portuguese english3_40a773cc:

    # "Isn't she married? I guess that doesn't stop some people."
    "Ela não é casada? Acho que isso não impede algumas pessoas."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:67
translate portuguese english3_2358e52d:

    # "Still though, she is a teacher. And older than me."
    "Ainda assim, ela é professora. E mais velha do que eu."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:68
translate portuguese english3_48dff846:

    # "Am I really into that?"
    "Será que gosto mesmo disso?"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:71
translate portuguese english3_c15f3a61:

    # "She is hot as fuck. I want to see what she has going on under those dresses that she always wears."
    "Ela é linda de morrer. Quero ver o que ela tem por baixo daqueles vestidos que usa sempre."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:75
translate portuguese english3_e434795b:

    # "She doesn't really have anything that interested me."
    "Na verdade, ela não tem nada que me interesse."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:76
translate portuguese english3_0cd18054:

    # "I try to push her out of my mind and concentrate on my classes."
    "Tento afastá-la da minha mente e concentrar-me nas aulas."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:77
translate portuguese english3_cf1b04ad:

    # "The rest of the day passes by uneventfully. Then I leave and go to work."
    "O resto do dia passa sem incidentes. Depois saio e vou para o trabalho."

